{"tid":1562248,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"搭車有個好臭嘅阿伯","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:56:53.000Z","uid":271835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07f36320884b9fe9f544566d750710f6b6706897","tid":1562248,"uid":271835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，I go to work by bus<br />\n最近因為個個唔撚搭党鐵逼哂去巴士，有時返工要焗住坐落下層<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落車前尾二個站成日有個阿伯（唔知是咪廢老啦）都唔知幾多個月冇沖過涼，一上車就會搞到成個下層都係屎坑味<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n臭到要我頂兩個站都唔多掂<br />\n仲要佢會狙擊關愛座一人霸兩位，我以後都唔敢坐呢條線嘅關愛座<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我好想下次一見到佢準備上車就一個箭步衝埋去，塞廿蚊俾佢叫佢一係返屋企沖個涼洗埋衫，一係搭下一班車<br />\n唔知各位巴打有冇好啲嘅方法令我唔使再喺車度見到佢<br />\n最好就係如果都知道係邊個阿伯，可以一齊集思吓點令佢唔好臭親人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌我而家喺公司都好似仲聞到陣屎味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6e519b930a569bb69cf87e6d33244c56621542","tid":1562248,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:48:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b854adb06806a971b69a6813c757fc0682ad2fdc","tid":1562248,"uid":271234,"like"